message.body: Hey sunshine!
Aw so sorry to miss you! I was in yoga. Probably doing something ridiculous. Yoga is so funny sometimes. :)
You almost missed me but not quite....just on the verge of losing my signal
Can you actually talk?
No honey .....not a strong enough signal here and I have to be back into the monastery before lights out at 9:30.....
But I wanted to let you know I truly miss you ♡
You've gotta go! 7 minutes! Sleep well. :)
Aw you made a little heart!
The dream next week please!!
Ok I will.....
Also I may come to Thursday clinic this week. I want to makeup the time I will miss in Maine preemptively...
I did make a l'il heart! Roo roo!
And i'd like to cone Saturday if we can be a couple. Okay with you? Me + You vs. Jason! Lol
Yes please come be my date!
It's a date! Sweet dreams precious girl! ♡ ♡
I sent him an email explaining I really do want to understand and he said he would talk to me thurs or sat so I'm gonna try to catch him between clinic and lunch.
Do you actually sleep more at the monastery?
Is that a joke! :-) No I read and meditate while these punks sleep!
You're funny! I thought they might make you lie down! Ha ha
It's your bedtime. Love, M
Ok.....losing signal! Sleep snug as a bug in a rug! The Jason thing sounds great!
Bye for now ....
Love, Keithers
Ps: I am going to see Laura in NYC next weekend! Emailing with her now. So excited....
I always call you!!!
Are you around?
Tried to call to say hi.
Sorry....the phone died:'(
I can talk now if you can
Lunch tomorrow??? :) :) I want to hear more about what you do in NY!!
Sorry I had to rush off.....I was standing at the door and thought I had a few minutes but bill opened the door and I was assaulted by dogs and Bill!!! :
-) :-) I love you
We never ever have enough time! Your telephone habits are a bit like a teenage girl's, which I am grateful for. :) :)
No to lunch? A rain check then?
If I wear Keith dress to school on a Thursday can we get Chinese for dinner again someday?
Sorry....I didn't see the lunch text! His bout the Keith dress and i treat to dinner at Chinese next Thursday? Date?

Can we do two weeks from now? May 30? Are you free? I'm coming back to clinic this Thursday to work with Tara. Keith dress is too scandalous for clinic PLUS I will be with Laura on the 26 and can fill you in with sixth ray ferver. You will tell me about
Plus you will be cutting so I won't try to poke at you. :)
Ok....as long as we can have a date before then ......I'm spoiled now! :-) :-)
Lunch then! Next Thursday after clinic????
I'm literally writing you in to my calendar for the 30th for a dinner date. :)
Yes....Thursday it is..moratorium on school talk.....
And moratorium on cream cheese slides for desert .... ugh
Ooh! That means we have two weeks in a row of food dates! Yes! I'm writing that down too. For reals!
This semester is going to fly by! Pierces class is 40% over!!!!
For reals! Both! I'm looking forward to them both!
Me too!!!!
Thank you Keith!
Thank YOU, Monica
heart heart my friend
I will still wear something cute next Thursday. It won't be as cute as Keith dress but it will be good.
I like liking you....even if you say I have girl telephone habits and am squishy at the edges
Oh Keith. Thank you. I like you even if you tell me I have terrible taste in men and Tansy.
I'll look forward to both! Especially what has now famously been coined the Keith dress!
You will like it. It is lovely.
Like you.
You do and do....:-) :-)
Roo and roo?
I do and do what??
And you are lovely too......very very
Thank you sweet one.
It's probably true but I would want to keep you in bulking phase to make a little pillow top mattress for me to rest on. :)
Ok......now we're gonna have to break up. Lol
Lucky for you, Joy does not seem to mind hard surfaces. :)
Ah well....we had a good run
That made me laugh
Ryan told me treating patients is the most magnificent thing he's ever done.
What the pillow top made you laugh?
She gave up trying to figure out my idiosyncracies with body image issues long ago!! :-)
Joy is good like that!
I have my own little things too.
Plus I've gotta point out that you can take the girl out of west Philly but you can't take the west Philly out of the girl.....
Yes....and the hard surfaces .....
And just so you know....I weigh about 210.....when I met her i was 145
You have things? :-)
Ryan is .........ryan
I know allllllll about west Philly
Oh a littler Keith!!! Can I see photos?
Yep Ryan is Ryan all right. Seriously you would tell me if I was mentally ill or otherwise in trouble right? Even if my face was super sad?
I have so few pictures.....im not so brave
Between six one and six two and 145 is pretty bad....my waist was like 28.....now its 31 or 32
Yes altho its not like I'm a psychotherapist .....but you're not. :-) :-)
Just checking cause thats me....but we're okay right......the discussion about boundaries and you feeling ok with me and me insisting im not Ryan.....on and on
Well.......personally I don't think you're pathetic at all......I understand the little toes dilemma .......and that's HIS loss....and when it comes to m
e.....you picked someone who feels the same as you and who truly and deeply loves you right back.....
You're easy to love....
I have about 5 years to have a baby!
Well.......I'm not gay! :-) :-)
Do you usually find those two separate?
Yep! If you figured out what to do about this, please full me in over lunch next week! For real!!!
What's about "this"?
I need to start thinking about sleep! Will you try to protect my seat beside you in the morning? Like spread out your stuff like a sloppy ass earth cf and save one for me!?
I'm taking the train that arrived at 8:31.
Yes..I'll save your seat! :-)
Woot woot! Goodnight Keith.
Omg you have to tell me soon please! Really do tell me! I keep remembering at odd times about your dreams....
Laura worked with dreams at the December training and my dreams have been more amazing since then! I have to tell you about the dreams I have about Laura on occasion.
Definitely have to remember to talk about them when we're in tge same room together! :-)
Ok...good. sweetest of dreams tonight! Mrow!
Roo roo
Really? Thats interesting!
Yes! I will tell you when we meet to talk dream work. I swear it!
That's great! Deal!
Ok....great!
Thank you for (beginning to) share your dream with me.
It is deeper and to me shows that connection interiorly....
Yes. I agree.
On the train with Stephanie and Rachael (gasp!!!) till 8:35 then home right around 9 or 9:15. Talk then?? xoxoxo
XOXOXO
Hey sweetpea. I'm home now!
I'll text or call in a few, okay? Getting through bill's evening routine....<3
Ok!
Call please! :)
Ok!
Almost there with Bill?
Almost honey....like five minutes
Thanks Keith. Call when you can.
Good morning Keith! :) :)
Good morning, Monica. I'm at the emergency room....had to come over at 3am for chest pain.
Oh no!
No....it's the fluid in my chest from the congestive heart failure stuff
:( If you give me a bendy straw I could come drink that out for you. You know I would too. :)
You would hate it because they tell me it tastes like chocolate peanut butter cups..who likes that?
Do you know that I smeared chocolate pb granola bar on my lab coat the very first day of clinic? lol
No but I know you like to wet your lab coat down at school and hang it on the back of a chair in Les' class
My lab coat likes showers instead of baths.
I'm sorry you're in the ER dear one.
With or without botanical soap?
Soap free like me
It's ok....... it'll mean a trip to NY as soon as I get out so that I can get cheaper treatment ...
NY is like your own personal Canada for healthcare. :)
NY is good but that means no cell service! I'm glad we got to talk last night.
Without the Canadian or Ohion accents...
I love my accent. :)
I can never understand you......
What! Haha I fell for that for a moment.
Especially after wine and Anne's cookies ...the accent gets heavier
Yep. :)
Haha
That is hard to imagine :-) :-)
I love you. Please be well.
I love you too. I will.
An impressive introduction
I was thinking about how you said Les loves me and I think that he can see into me a little bit like you can. That's the biggest honor--to be seen.
That's what we're all kinda looking for...
Yes. I appreciate that about our relationship. You can see down into the silt and the clear water at the bottom of the beautiful lake.
I do appreciate us....
Me too
Good luck with Clinic ....I'm off to x ray
Thanks Keith. I love you. Good luck with the X-ray. Please help me protect you at school--no more heart points and very simple txs only.
Are you ok?
Almost in NY. Clinic ok?

I left you a voicemail. It was ok (no tears) just incredibly hard. I don't know anything. I worked with Lisa which was good but I designed a really weird tx. It felt weird and random to me. It's hard to connect to your treatments when you don't really und
Tried to call a couple times be fore i lose my signal
Aw I was underground on the trolley! Call if you get a signal again!!

Everyone was ok with you bringing bill this Saturday and us working together. I just have to check the schedule and make sure I don't have a returning patient. Also if you want to come sat June 1 I have a friend coming in. We could work together.
I know you won't get this till later but Goodnight Keithers!!
